Egyptian Ptolemaic Kingdom coinage is amazing! 🏒 This 68.5 gram drachm feels like a heavy rock or a hockey puck lol! Crispy large portrait of Zeus Ammon on the front & the classic eagle standing on a thunderbolt on the reverse. It also features another example of the circle indentations usually found on Ptolemaic coinage which is thought to be from preparation of the coin. #ptolemaickingdom #ancientcoin #ancientcoins #ancientart #headyart

//“Dimensional Shifter” #9//✨now sold (Link in @VINHWINH bio) DM for inquiries
Have you ever seen Infinity? 🤔♾ The concept of anything existing or going on for forever is something that in our scope is a little hard to imagine... well here’s a look at a visual representation of Infinity in the form of glass a light, this piece has some of the most #dimensional quality from a Shifter so far, one look through it’s portal sends you into an infinite spectrum of light and color! 🤩🌈✨
💎💎💎
SWIPE LEFT for detail shots
This “Dimensional Shifter” #9 features some of my Dimensional glass under an all #freehandfaceted cut and polish for that Crystal aesthetic and comes with a .925 Sterling Silver chain.. this double-sided piece looks great front either side, be sure to Swipe Left for a Front/Back view and to see detail shots of this piece! which side do you like more?!
